I’ve been through five startups in my career and Apptio is by far the most exciting and promising one of the bunch. From the people to the technology to the market opportunity, everything is top notch. From a technical standpoint, the work is very challenging and demanding, yet we pay more than lip service to work/life balance
Supin Ko
Software Development Engineering Manager
 





I love working at Apptio because the culture is fantastic. You’re learning constantly and it’s fast-paced! As a young professional, it’s been especially exciting and rewarding to be involved in the future design and development of Apptio products. Having said this, what I love most about Apptio are the people I get to work with on the daily. I love my team! Nerf guns anyone?!
Shelby Nuccitelli
Application Engineer
 


