I joined Apptio a year ago where we were less than 150 employees. I have been enjoying being part of the growth and success of Apptio. I feel like we are a family animated by the same passion. In a year I was able to evolve into a new position with more management. Apptio gave me the opportunity to challenge myself and to always want to do better always with a smile! So if I have to describe Apptio I would say: great work environment, great people (including leadership), and opportunities to grow and be part of something big!
Nora Paxton 
