You are hereHomeAboutCompany 








The business management system of record for hybrid IT
Apptio transforms the way IT runs its business and makes decisions. With our cloud-based applications, IT leaders manage, plan and optimize their technology investments across on-premises and cloud. With Apptio, IT leaders become strategic partners to the business by demonstrating value of IT investments, accelerating innovation and shifting their technology investments from running the business to digital innovation.
 Background Image: 

 








default-padding We help CIOs to make fact-based decisions and plan for the future.
White







Our Cost Transparency, IT Planning, IT Benchmarking, Bill of IT and Business Insights SaaS applications align technology investments to business priorities, engage business stakeholders to drive accountability and value, and optimize and increase efficiency of hybrid IT resources.
 Apptio is the only solution that automatically aggregates, cleanses and establishes relationships across large amounts of data from disparate financial, operational and vendor invoices, and maps that data into our standard IT cost model. With Apptio, IT can shift 3-5% of their spending over five years into innovation strategically aligned with the broader goals of the business.
Whiteno-top-padding 00




00bg-gray-lightest Light Gray


REQUIRED
Just as sales has CRM and finance has ERP, today’s IT leaders need a business management system to measure technology investments, plan for the future, and communicate the business value of IT. Apptio unlocks existing financial, operational, and billing data from on-premises and cloud providers to serve as the single source of truth across the business. 
0000 





INSIGHTFUL
Apptio helps IT leaders make data-driven business decisions by providing analytics and insights into the cost, quality, and value of IT.  We combine powerful analytics with process workflow to empower CIOs and their teams with the deep insights they need in order to make great data-driven decisions. We offer five packaged SaaS applications that lead to valuable insights within 90 days.
0000 





HYBRID
Cloud has introduced a new business model for IT, increasing complexity and opening new opportunities for IT to deliver innovation in support of business objectives. Only Apptio provides a full view of technology investments across on-premises, public cloud, private cloud, infrastructure, applications, business services, and projects.
0cta-center000 





TRUSTED
Today, hundreds of global enterprise organizations, across all sizes and verticals, manage their IT business with Apptio, including 40% of the Fortune 100.  We are also the founder of the nonprofit TBM Council, now with more than 3,000 members. It is the largest global professional organization of IT leaders dedicated to TBM.
0cta-center000 


2 Columns




Whether you need help understanding the true cost of the cloud, optimizing your technology spending or communicating IT's value to the business, Apptio can help.
Get Started
